sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client/Browser
    participant API as Flask API<br/>(app.py)
    participant FalkorDB as FalkorDB<br/>(falkordb service)
    participant Qdrant as Qdrant<br/>(qdrant service)
    
    Note over Client,Qdrant: Health Check (No Auth Required)
    Client->>API: GET /health
    API->>FalkorDB: PING
    FalkorDB-->>API: PONG
    API->>Qdrant: GET /healthz
    Qdrant-->>API: 200 OK
    API-->>Client: 200 {"status": "healthy",<br/>"falkordb": "connected",<br/>"qdrant": "connected"}
    
    Note over Client,Qdrant: Test Memory Storage (Auth Required)
    Client->>API: POST /memory<br/>Authorization: Bearer TOKEN<br/>{"content": "test"}
    API->>FalkorDB: MERGE (m:Memory)
    FalkorDB-->>API: memory_id
    API->>Qdrant: upsert(id, vector)
    Qdrant-->>API: success
    API-->>Client: 201 {"memory_id": "...",<br/>"status": "success"}